<html lang='en'>

<head>
  <meta charset='UTF-8' />
  <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    .container {
      width: 80%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .info,
    .booking-details,
    .footer {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .info p,
    .booking-details p,
    .footer p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #555555;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .booking-details h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: start;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .footer b {
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      border-bottom: 1px double #000;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class='header'>
      <h1>TH Global Travel</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='info'>

      <p><strong>Dear </strong> {{fullName}},</p>
      <p>Thank you for reaching out to TH Global Travel with your recent enquiry. We are delighted to assist you in
        planning your upcoming trip and provide you with all the necessary details for a memorable travel experience.
      </p>
      <p>Based on the information provided, here are the details of the requested tour:</p>

      <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
      <p><strong>Phone:</strong> {{phone}}</p>
      <p><strong>Country:</strong> {{country}}</p>
      <p><strong>Travel Dates:</strong> {{date}}</p>
    </div>
    <div class='booking-details'>
      <h2>{{tourName}}</h2>
      <p><strong>Quantity:</strong> {{quantity}}</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> {{price}}</p>
      <p><strong>Other request:</strong> {{otherRequest}}</p>
      <p><strong>Total Price After Discount Applied :</strong> {{calculateDiscountedPriceForTour quantity price
        discount}}</p>
      <p>Please note that the availability of your requested tour package is subject to confirmation by our sales team.
        Once we verify the availability, we will promptly inform you and proceed with the booking process.</p>
      <p>If you have any specific preferences or additional requirements, please let us know so that we can tailor the
        tour to meet your needs. Our goal is to ensure you have a seamless and enjoyable travel experience with TH
        Global Travel.</p>
      <p>Thank you once again for choosing TH Global Travel. We look forward to making your travel dreams a reality.</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
    </div>
    <div class='footer'>
      <b style='text-transform: uppercase;'>TH Global Travel</b>
      <p>Hotline:<a href='tel:+84946707266'>+84946707266</a></p>
      <p>Email: <a href='mailto:info@thglobaltravel.com'>info@thglobaltravel.com</a></p>
      <p>Website: <a href='https://thglobaltravel.com/'>thglobaltravel.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>